= Blackhawk Realm / Schwarzhabichtreich =

A nation in a different Earth with slightly different countries, the Blackhawk Realm attempts to cement itself as a superpower under novudeism. Its land in Europe is France, Switzerland, Benelux, Denmark, the German Empire, and Catalonia. The Realm is famed and founded on their brutality against those who they see as inferior, like most fascists. Unlike most fascists, however, the state is founded on a new and arbitrary race, state, and/or culture, with worse policies than normal fascism (not as bad as Nazism). This creates a new ideology: novudeism (from Latin novus deus, new day). It includes Aquilanians, Velanidians, Aetherlanders, Lavanese, northeastern Spadacians, and mainland European North Seians.
